{"tid":2065061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【叫雞唔畀錢】旺角男用假銀終叫雞，先剝光豬，後裸跑","createTime":"2020-06-15T09:13:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T07:42:05.000Z","uid":202464,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"6cf9fd9edcc86899940906888f15678d40371801","tid":2065061,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T09:13:35.000Z","msg":"1. 拖男祼跑片近日在網上瘋傳。片段中男子在拍攝者指示下，手持衣物，全身僅穿著一對人字拖，從後巷步出沿旺角塘尾道行走，沿途經過住宅、汽車維修店，<br />\n<br />\n2. 據街坊所講，上址一帶除了一家卡啦ok夜總會外，不見有色情場所，但相信男子不是光顧該夜總會：「如果係，佢（被打到）落唔到樓。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 男子不斷被拍片者以粗口辱罵，被指示旺角塘尾道「兜個圈」，他走至大街時吸引途人目光時，拍片者喊道：「唔好望呢啲人渣嚟，X你老X用假銀紙叫雞喎，都夠膽死，肉金都X你老X呃啲X家X！」<br />\n<br />\n到達塘尾道218號對開，指示男子「轉個彎著返衫，跑過去嗰度轉個彎，快啲啦！」"},{"pid":"bb28f3b3cc69cd09f7b36654445c1090b1416dfe","tid":2065061,"uid":202464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T09:15:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HWrwAzD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHWrwAzD.jpg&h=f5edddef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3422178cd91f8fd86b469cd74b090165a8c8833a","tid":2065061,"uid":335434,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T09:16:46.000Z","msg":"唔記得帶委任證同真銀紙嘅休班警?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20ceccecb6bde89e82824eeaf2b76429b2f9d73d","tid":2065061,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T09:17:23.000Z","msg":"真警"},{"pid":"7deae7ddbefd817ba281d66020c4f9c8b810d793","tid":2065061,"uid":14103,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T09:17:38.000Z","msg":"隻雞好貴咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efda